Package smarthome.persistence.datamodel.mapper

Class ActuatorModelDataModelMapper

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.datamodel.mapper.ActuatorModelDataModelMapper
@Component public class ActuatorModelDataModelMapper extends Object
This class is responsible for mapping between the ActuatorModelDataModel and the ActuatorModel domain object. It uses the ActuatorModelFactory to create instances of ActuatorModel.
